			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				How to finish the quest.<BR>
I just finished the Wurmslayer quest. So here is how you should do to complete it.<BR>
<BR>
1. How to get the scales are well explained in posts above.<BR>
2.Once you got your 3 scales go to Firiona Vie and look for Sir Hobble, a paladin.<BR>
3. He spawns in the area west of the river so run araound in that area until you find him. <BR>
4. If he allready has spawned he start fighting every creature he finds and starts walking arond all over FV. If this is the fact you will need someone to track him. But so far what I have seen, he is walking around mainly in the south half of FV. I have never seen him in the north part. It is not confirmed if he only walks around in South FV.<BR>
5. Once you find Hobble, Hail him. He will then call for Squire Fuzzmin who will spawn in east FV (not confirmed) and start running to Hobble(confirmed). So be patient and follow Hobble after you have hailed him and Squire will eventually arrive if he doesnt get killed on the way.<BR>
6. Once Squire has arrived to Hobble they will walk together all the time. The easiest way to hand over the scales to Squire is when he is fighting because then he is standing still. You can do it when he is walking, I did, but it is a bit harder.<BR>
7. Voila !!! Wurmslayer and some xp!<BR>
<BR>
Dimytes lvl 32 Paladin on Innoruuk.
